title: Pixel 4 calendar not syncing with outlook calendar
content:
I have checked to ensure account is the same as on my PC. 
I have removed the account and re-installed
I checked my tablet and the detail looks the same and it is working fine as far as syncing.

Still does not sync? Is this a flaw with Android 10 or is there something I am missing. Was thinking of a factory reset and starting all over again but would rather not take that route.

Any help out there?  Thanking you in advance.
